{"tid":147512,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"良心 LG 為舊機 G4、V10 提供升級","createTime":"2017-03-08T01:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T06:18:04.000Z","uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40e6796ec925cf0657549a94bb85c7e55e54bfed","tid":147512,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:55:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>良心 LG 為舊機 G4、V10 提供升級</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/0307-3a-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F0307-3a-1.jpg&h=2d640d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一部上市至今已經 2 年的手機，一般情況下已經被手機品牌列為停產，並且停止提供系統更新和支援。不過 LG 就為消費者帶來好消息，日前透過官方網誌宣佈，將會為 2015 年 4 月和 10 月發表的 G4 和 V10 手機，提供 Android 7.0 Nougat 系統更新。<br />\n<br />\nLG 在網誌內表示，兩款手機在 Android 5.0 和 6.0 系統會獲得最佳的表現，但為了尊重用戶的選擇權，最後經過慎重考慮後決定為 G4 和 V10 提供系統更新。首先得到系統更新的將會是較新的 LG V10，預計會在今年第二季獲得升級；至於 LG G4 則要等到今年第三季。不過 LG 重申今次升級安排只限韓國本土，國際版本將另行宣佈。"},{"pid":"d63ae496c36144c30f4b2aa95b7a8dfbb69cc1ca","tid":147512,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:56:00.000Z","msg":"不過... 塊底版捱唔捱到果日都成問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e516d9bfeadd8fcccb28b4a91aa512269635be","tid":147512,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:57:36.000Z","msg":"不過 LG 重申今次升級安排只限韓國本土，國際版本將另行宣佈。<br />\n<br />\n港行睇黎都係無份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b75814ec92f6798e5b778e4f6258d1b46a6477b","tid":147512,"uid":83754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"舊機升軟件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3ea9ced6362681ee35f0ffeb773301b0cd10c2","tid":147512,"uid":54455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:59:12.0